rwg goNf iv`c BgqW dI bwxI[(rwg goNf)
Gr 1 iv`c Bgq kbIr jI dI bwxI[
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
jy koeI Blw mnu`K iml pey qW (aus dI is`iKAw) suxnI cwhIdI hY, qy (jIvn dy rwh dIAW guMJlW) pu`CxIAW cwhIdIAW hn[
pr jy koeI BYVw bMdw iml pey, qW au~Qy cu`p rihxw hI TIk hY ]1]
hy BweI! (jgq ivc rihMidAW) ikho ijhy bol bolIey,
ijn@W dI brkiq nwl prmwqmw dy nwm ivc surq itkI rhy? (not: bwkI dy swry Sbd ivc ies pRSn dw au~qr hY) ]1] rhwau]
(ikauNik) BilAW nwl g`l kIiqAW koeI BlweI dI g`l inklygI,
qy mUrK nwl boilAW ivArQ Kp-Kpw hI hovygw ]2]
(iPr) ijauN ijauN (mUrK nwl) g`lW krIey (aus dy kusMg ivc) ivkwr hI ivkwr vDdy hn; (pr ies dw Bwv ieh nhIN ik iksy nwl BI bihxw-Kloxw nhIN cwhIdw)[
jy Bly mnu`KW nwl BI nhIN bolWgy, (Bwv, jy BilAW pws BI nhIN bYTWgy) qW ivcwr dIAW g`lW ikvyN kr skdy hW? ]3]
hy kbIr! s`cI g`l ieh hY ik (ijvyN) ^wlI GVw boldw hY, jy auh (pwxI nwl) BirAw hoieAw hovy qW auh kdy foldw nhIN (iesy qrHW bhuqIAW &wlqU g`lW gux-hIn mnu`K hI krdw hY[
jo guxvwn hY auh Afol rihMdw hY[ so, jgq ivc koeI AYsw au~dm krIey, ijs nwl gux igRhx kr sikey, qy ieh gux iml skdy hn BilAW pwsoN hI) ]4]1]
xxx
(mYnUM kdy soc hI nhIN PurdI ik mYN iks srIr qy mwx kr ky mMdy kMm krdw rihMdw hW, myrw Aslw qW iehI hY nw ik) jdoN mnu`K mr jWdw hY qW mnu`K (dw srIr) iksy kMm nhIN AwauNdw,
pr pSU mrdw hY qW (iPr BI aus dw srIr mnu`K dy) keI kMm svwrdw hY ]1]
hy bwbw! mYN kdy socdw hI nhIN ik mYN ikho ijhy in`q-krm krI jw irhw hW, (mYN mMdy pwsy hI l`gw rihMdw hW, qy)
mYnUM ^iAwl hI nhIN AwauNdw ]1] rhwau]
(hy bwbw! mYN kdy soicAw hI nhIN ik mOq AwieAW ies srIr dIAW) h`fIAW l`kVW dy Fyr vWg sV jWdIAW hn,
qy (ies dy) kys Gwh dy pUly vWG sV jWdy hn (qy ijs srIr dw mgroN ieh hwl huMdw hY, ausy au~qy mYN swrI aumr mwx krdw rihMdw hW) ]2]
pr, hy kbIr! s`c ieh hY ik mnu`K ies mUrKqw vloN qdoN hI jwgdw hY (qdoN hI pCqwauNdw hY)
jdoN mOq dw fMfw ies dy isr au~qy Aw v`jdw hY ]3]2]
xxx
(ieh ijMd ijs dw AMS hY auh) cyqn-s`qw AkwS qoN pqwl q`k hr pwsy mOjUd hY[
auhI (jIvW dy) suK dw mUl-kwrn hY[ auh sdw kwiem rihx vwlw hY, auh hI (hY ijs nUM) au~qm purK (prmwqmw khIdw) hY[ (jIvW dw) srIr nws ho jWdw hY, pr (srIr ivc v`sdI ijMd dw somw) cyqn-s`qw nws nhIN huMdI ]1]
myry mn iv`c (hornW g`lW vloN) auprwmqw ho rhI hY, (mYnUM hor g`lW ZYr-zrUrI jwpdIAW hn[)
myrw inScw hux ies g`l au~qy itk igAw hY ik ieh ijMd kdy mrdI nhIN (ikauNik ieh ijMd aus srb-ivAwpk sdw-iQr cyqn-s`qw dw AMS hY) ]1] rhwau]
pMjW q`qW ny iml ky ieh srIr bxwieAw hY (pr iehnW q`qW dI BI koeI v`KrI hsqI nhIN hY), ieh q`q BI hor ik`QoN bxny sn? (ieh BI cyqn-s`qw qoN hI bxy hn)[
qusIN lok ieh AwKdy ho ik jIvwqmw kIqy krmW krmW dw b`Jw hoieAw hY, (pr Asl g`l ieh hY ik) krmW nUM BI pihlW cyqn-s`qw qoN ibnw hor iks ny vjUd ivc ilAwauxw sI? (Bwv, krmW nUM BI pihlW ieh cyqn-s`qw hI vjUd ivc ilAwauNdI hY) ]2]
hy BweI! aus cyqn-s`qw pRBU dy AMdr ieh (jIvW dw) srIr vjUd ivc AwauNdw hY, qy srIrW ivc auh pRBU v`sdw hY[ sBnW dy AMdr auhI hY, ikqy iv`Q nhIN hY[
so, kbIr AwKdw hY-AYsy cyqn-s`qw prmwqmw dw nwm mYN kdy nhIN BulwvWgw, (nwm ismrn dI brkiq nwl hI ieh smJ AwauNdI hY ik) jo kuJ jgq ivc ho irhw hY suqy hI (aus cyqn-s`qw pRBU dI rzw ivc) ho irhw hY ]3]3]
rwg goNf, Gr 2 iv`c Bgq kbIr jI dI bwxI[
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
myrIAW bwhW bMnH ky Fym vWg (mYnUM iehnW lokW hwQI A`gy) su`t id`qw hY,
(mhwvq ny) gu`sy ivc Aw ky hwQI dy isr au~qy (s`t) mwrI hY[
pr hwQI (mYnUM pYrW hyT ilqwVn dy QW) cIkW mwr ky (hor pwsy) B`jdw hY,
(ijvyN AwKdw hY-) mYN sdky hW ies sohxy bMdy qoN ]1]
hy myry pRBU! mYnUM qyrw qwx hY (so, qyrI brkiq nwl mYnUM koeI i&kr nhIN hY)[
kwzI qW kih irhw hY ik (ies kbIr au~qy) hwQI cwVH dyh ]1] rhwau]
(kwzI AwKdw hY-) nhIN qW mYN qyrw isr auqrw idAWgw,
ies hwQI nUM s`t mwr qy (kbIr vl) qor[
pr hwQI qurdw nhIN (auh qW ieauN id`sdw hY ijvyN) pRBU-crnW ivc msq hY,
(ijvyN) aus dy ihrdy ivc prmwqmw (prgt ho ky) v`s irhw hY ]2]
Blw mYN Awpxy pRBU dy syvk ny iehnW dw kIh ivgwV kIqw sI?
jo myrI potlI bMnH ky (iehnW mYnUM) hwQI A`gy su`t id`qw[
(BwvyN ik) hwQI (myry srIr dI bxI) potlI nUM muV muV isr invw irhw hY,
pr kwzI nUM (quA`sb dy) hnyry ivc ieh smJ hI nhIN AweI ]3]
(kwzI ny hwQI nUM myry aupr cwVH cwVH ky) iqMn vwrI prqwvw ilAw,
